==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stupor
<hw>Stu"por</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., from
<ets>stupere</ets> to be struck senseless.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Great
diminution or suspension of sensibility; suppression of sense or
feeling; lethargy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Intellectual insensibility; moral stupidity;
heedlessness or inattention to one's interests.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stupose</ent>⟦br⟧
